   :topic: Chapter2/OperatorsforCharacters
   :from_source: T
   :language: cpp
   :caption: Automatic Type Conversion

   This program performs automatic type converstion.  It converts 'a'
   to its ASCII value.
   ~~~~
   #include <iostream>
   using namespace std;

   int main () {
       int number;
       number = 'a';
   }
